        <p>This "Barcode Filing Management System (BFMS)" project was successfully completed by <strong>NEOH WEI JIAN</strong> at the <strong>Faculty of Intelligent Computing, Universiti Malaysia Perlis (UniMAP)</strong>, as part of their Diploma Engineering (Computer Engineering) final year project. BFMS is dedicated to providing an efficient, reliable, and user-friendly book management solution for educational environments.</p>
