        <p>Our goal is to streamline book organization, enhance real-time tracking capabilities, improve user experience through an intuitive interface, ensure data security with access control, and provide a scalable system for growing book volumes. By automating filing, borrowing, and retrieval processes, BFMS aims to significantly reduce manual overhead, minimize errors, and boost operational efficiency.</p>
